INSTALL

System-wide install:
Extract this archive to $KDE4ROOT/share/apps/desktoptheme directory,
where $KDE4ROOT is the location where your KDE4.0 is installed.

User-only install:
Extract this archive to ~/.kde4/share/apps/desktoptheme directory

HOW TO ACTIVATE

Open your plasmarc file (~/.kde4/share/config/plasmarc) and in the
[Theme] section replace name=Default with name=silicon

When you restart plasma, the new theme will be loaded.
(you can log out, and log back in)

In newer Versions of plasma you can select it through the appearance plasma dialog.

